high_descs: Walk forward four steps, turn left for four steps and stop to the left of the toilet.
Pick up the plunger from the floor, between the sink and the toilet.
Turn around and walk three steps, turn around again and face the sink.
Open the left cabinet door under the sink, place the plunger in the cabinet on the front right.
anns.task_desc: Put a plunger in the cabinet beneath the sink

high_descs: Move forward towards the shower stall then turn left and face the sink.
Pick up the turquoise toilet plunger from the floor between the sink and the toilet.
Turn around and move towards the bathroom door then turn around and face the bathroom vanity.
Open the vanity cabinet door beneath the sink closest to the toilet, place the plunger in front of the green soap dispenser bottle, and then close the vanity cabinet door.
anns.task_desc: Place a toilet plunger in the bathroom vanity.
